description: [PR Newswire] - LONGUEUIL, QC, Dec. 12, 2016 /CNW Telbec/ - Innergex Renewable Energy Inc. (INE.TO) ("Innergex" or the "Corporation") is pleased to announce that agreements have been signed for the acquisition of two wind power projects with a total capacity of 24 MW located in Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France. Innergex will own a 69.55% interest in the project and the Régime de rentes du Mouvement Desjardins ("RRMD") will own the remaining 30.45%.
